   GORE-NH _ WASHINGTON _ With Big Labor behind his campaign in
other early states, Vice President Al Gore is turning his attention
to a suddenly neck-and-neck New Hampshire primary race with former
Sen. Bill Bradley. (Shepard, Cox News Service) MOVED in (w)
