<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-BOHEME-OPERA-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   BOHEME-OPERA-REVIEW (New York) will not move in tonight's New
York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Oct. 17.
</P>
</TEXT>
