<TEXT>
<P>
   WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ A Palm Beach County Sheriff's detective
posed as ``Sagster002,'' a 15-year-old boy, in an online
conversation with ``Thefortres,'' or James Fortier, 40, of West
Palm Beach. Fortier pleaded guilty Aug. 25 to solicitation of a
child for sex by use of a computer. Here are excerpts from their
